    {
        "url": "/quotes/sugata_mitra_554143",
        "quote": "I was inspired by the Hole in the Wall project, where a computer with an internet connection was put in a Delhi slum. When the slum was revisited after a month, the children of that slum had learned how to use the worldwide web.",
